story: Mohamed Abdel-Gawad shared his post to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Mohamed
description:
Very Urgent Vacancies:
 2- iPhone IOS Developer - Junior 
Skills & Requirements: 
• University degree in the field of computer science, information science. 
• 2+ years’ experience developing apps for IOS and at least 2 app in the App Store (yours or one you worked on) 
• Intermediate to expert level skills in Objective-C development and good knowledge of the IOS SDK and XCODE. 
• Passion and appreciation for great design and exceptional UI/UX. 
• Experience in deployment to the app store and setting up provisions/certification. 
• Intermediate skills in data structures such as XML and JSON. 

Send CVs to: m.gawad@ebeshara.com
